advise? <p>Baron <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=339346">Vladius Solarwind</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
60th level Sorceror of Solusek Ro<br>
Member of <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.geocities.com/vcrusaders/">Valiant Crusaders</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
-Ayonae Ro<br>
<br>
